1.title: Contact
1.plot: While Evert and Bram become involuntarily involved in a spectacular escape, clashes Fenna hard with the police after a brutal murder that could have been prevented in her eyes. Dries gets a desperate request from an old friend.

2.title: Blackout
2.plot: Fenna's conflict with the police threatens to escalate. Bram is now planning a bold plan and Liselotte is looking for the mysterious extortioner of Wolter and calls for help from outside. The hacker shows what he is capable of.

3.title: Beertje bashen
3.plot: Evert tries to find out as much as possible about the mysterious woman. Liselotte fights the hacker online when he commits a new attack. Her team members now coordinate a daring break-in, but it is completely out of hand. After a gruesome discovery, they realize that the enemy may be closer than they thought.

4.title: Face to face
4.plot: A new visit to Naomi brings Evert in big problems. Fenna wants to meet Bo. Liselotte seeks contact with the murderous hacker and makes an appointment for which she can not oversee the consequences.

5.title: Strak schema
5.plot: The relationships within the team are put to the test by a loss. Dries is fiercely tested and Fenna decides to dive into the archives. Time to put things in a row is not there: the killer has already chosen his next target.

6.title: Stella
6.plot: A discovery by Bo offers the team a great opportunity. Fenna sees through a ruse. Dries makes a drastic decision. Evert has an unexpected meeting, while Ligtveld is after the team.

7.title: Vergif
7.plot: Now that her teammates have been arrested, there is nothing for Bo to do except to haul the murderous hacker out of his hole. Dries must confess something. Evert and Naomi put a bold plan into effect. Rossmann calls an important employee on the mat.

8.title: Zevende ster

1.title: Valse start
1.plot: On Fenna Kremers's first day as a detective in Leeuwarden, an offender escapes. It seems that this man would like revenge and there threatening to fall some victims if he don't found fast enough. Fenna's idiosyncratic way of working is not by all her new colleagues in the taste.

2.title: Rebecca
2.plot: During the Sneekweek there arrives a threatening letter at the headquarters. If certain requirements are not satisfied, there will be for the thousands visitors a deadly consequences. The team does everything to identify the sender of the letter and prevent an attack committed in Sneek.

3.title: Vuurduin
3.plot: Bram and Fenna travel to Vlieland when there's a body of a young man wash ashore. At first they suspected that the victim was beaten overboard. But then they discover that the boy had a reason to visit Vlieland. He was looking for something and he wasn't the only one.

4.title: Testfase
4.plot: During a burglary at a secondary school a locker is stolen, containing the national examinations that are about to begin. If the investigation team don't found the locker enough, there will be implications for thousands of high school students. Because of time pressure, tensions within the investigation team are high.

5.title: Eén voor allen
5.plot: The brothers Carlo and Olivier were held responsible for numerous violent crimes in Friesland for years. Until one day they disappeared and nobody heard anything from them. It seems that the brothers are back, when there find a violent raid takes place in a restaurant. And they came back for a special reason.

6.title: Teruggefloten
6.plot: In Leeuwarden there's a wooden box found with a amputated man's hand. Short after this there is found a second box with another part of a man's body. The detective team does everything what's possible to prevent even more boxes. But who is the perpetrator and what does he wants?

7.title: Hartpijn
7.plot: A boy and girl of seventeen are not returned from sailing at the IJsselmeer. The task for Fenna and Evert to immediate their family on the height. If the girl fished later that day she is still alive and well, meanwhile Fenna has discovered that there are strange things going on within her family.

8.title: Vermoorde onschuld
8.plot: In the Thialf Stadium is a charity hockey game between two teams but it is overshadowed by the murder of two boys from the youth selection. The offender is already arrested, but Fenna has serious doubts whether this man actually did it. Then there arrives someone from the past and again there lives at stakes.

9.title: Een oude bekende
9.plot: A dangerous criminal knows to escape during a transfer to Leeuwarden. If it appears that this man played a role in the history of Fenna and he now may be on its coined. The pressure to find this man grows. Through all this, Fenna confronted with memories she rather forget.

10.title: Alles op zijn tijd
10.plot: Fenna is in bad shape. She sits at home and it seems no one to contact her. As one of the other detectives announce to leave, Carla sees her team slowly disintegrate. Then Leeuwarden startled by a winding-reaching consequences.

1.title: Koud Kunstje
1.plot: In the center of the city their is left is a suitcase before the entrance of a hotel. The investigators suspect their are some explosives in the suitcase and let the whole neighborhood evacuate.

2.title: Een uniek exemplaar
2.plot: Evert is dating again, but it soon turns out that this woman has something to hide.

3.title: Bittere Pil
3.plot: There are young victims of false ecstasy pills that circulate in the nightlife. The team does everything to figure out where these pills come from. Meanwhile Menno has to make an important decision in his life that will haunt him long.

4.title: Stille wateren, diepe gronden
4.plot: During excavation work on a construction site their is find a coffin which contains the body of a woman who has been missing for years. All traces show that she is buried alive. Then at the same site several coffins excavated.

5.title: Moment van de waarheid
5.plot: A young woman's car is found by the side of the road, driven into a tree, but there is no trace of the woman. Nobody knows where she is or if she's hurt. Then, a strange movie appears on the Internet.

6.title: Bloedband
6.plot: A drunken man is found behind the wheel of his car near a gas station. The man had a gun on his lap and it looks like he was about the rob the pump. The police brings hem to the station and is shows Bram knows this man very well.

7.title: Over de doden niets dan goeds
7.plot: A woman is shot in the parking lot of a cemetery. The woman appear to be the black sheep of a wealthy family and has a relationship with the owner of an illegal poker club. It looks like she is a victim of a business conflict, but is she?

8.title: Trouw tot in de Eeuwigheid
8.plot: A marine is killed in a park in the early in the morning. When Fenna and Menno research his home they apprehend an intruder. The intruder knows narrowly to escape, but were was the intruder looking for and are there links to the murder?

9.title: Kinderspel
9.plot: After a illegal twin is missing, the team suspects that a gang of child traffickers are active. Evert and Fenna go undercover to find and arrest the child traffickers.

10.title: Het Beste van twee kwaden
10.plot: The police are tipped that a notorious assassin is located in a hotel nearby. The team keep a eye on the assassin.

1.title: Laatste vlucht
1.plot: A parachutist collapses on a terrace. It turns out that the parachute has not been opened. Fenna and her colleagues examine whether it is an accident or that there's more. Meanwhile, Fenna worried about her father and arise within the investigation team voltages not remain without consequences.

2.title: Recht in eigen hand
2.plot: A young girl is found dead in a forest. She is brought to life with multiple stab wounds. It appears that they have used GHB, but she was not raped. It seems that the offender was disturbed. When the police investigating the case, they discover that everyone has something to hide inside the closed village community.

3.title: Donkere diepte
3.plot: In a recreational lake a teenage girl is pulled while swimming under water and she will not come up. Her friends turn the police in which a search campaigns. Then comes a message inside that in a nearby lock a body was found. When Fenna and Evert look the found out that this isn't the missing girl, but a middle-aged woman.

4.title: De hond van de heide
4.plot: A body of man who has come to life by the attack of a dog is found in a moorland. Who owns this dog, and involves this an accident or a purposeful action? Meanwhile, there is an internal investigation conducted of the functioning of Fenna and that puts the focus on the relationships within the team.

5.title: Verloren jeugd
5.plot: A girl who is forced to work in prostitution manages to escape from the escape car. The police thinks to have with her an important witness in the hands. The girl is still too afraid to go into details. When she decide to talk, she receive a text message .

6.title: Blue
6.plot: A boy takes in a bank building an employee hostage. It soon becomes apparent that he isn't into the money, but he carries a terrible secret with him. To bring this situation to a satisfactory conclusion, Fenna Kremer has to make a decision that goes completely against her sense and it will haunt her for a long time.

7.title: Hard tegen hard
7.plot: If the team is faced with a corpse, it appears impossible to determine the cause of death. The coroner is a mystery. It's not just that one body, and the detective must compete with a killer who seems too smart to be caught. Eventually, the police will have no option but to lure the culprit out of their conference zone.

8.title: Kind van de rekening
8.plot: A sex year old boy runs away from home, leaving his parents desperate at home. A search came to nothing and the police start to worry about the child. The next morning, his teddy bear is found at the home of a convicted pedophile that recently is released.

9.title: De bekentenis
9.plot: Prosecutor Jelle van Santen gets late a visits from an intruder, who flees when the six year old daughter of Jelle unexpectedly appears. It seems to be a botched robbery to go, but Carla does not trust it and feel that Jelle is hiding something.

10.title: Een hoge prijs
10.plot: Fenna is not the old, after all the events and her colleagues disagree about whether she is able to do her job properly. While investigating a double murder old frustrations among colleagues stabbing themselves re-emerged and Carla must do everything possible to keep the team together.

1.title: Ontheemd
1.plot: The investigation is aware of one million deal that will take place in the underworld. Stand at the time of transfer them ready to catch the two parties in the act, but that is different than planned. Meanwhile, the team must set without Fenna. She has started a completely new life .

2.title: IJdele Hoop
2.plot: A newspaper boy gets the fright of his life when the front door of a house suddenly opens and he comes face to face with an elderly lady with a bloody scissor in her hands. Inside he finds a dead man who was stabbed. If the boy goes outside, the old woman is gone. The investigation team starts a quest.

3.title: Beschermengel
3.plot: An unknown figure punish antisocial behavior on the streets off by shooting people. The detectives must do everything to find this man and prevent him or her from making even more victims. If they are using video images were able to determine his identity, one of the team members show the offender to know personally.

4.title: Oog om Oog
4.plot: A boy is kidnapped on the street after a hockey game. Police have no clue and it is waiting for a ransom demand. But that does not come. The team task in the darkness about why the boy is taken. Then there is suspicion toward his parents. They they know more?

5.title: Eigen Richting
5.plot: Two gay men do not have it easy in the district where they live. They get insults at their head , their house is plastered and the tires of their car are multiply slashed. One evening it went terribly out of hand, when the two guys confronted with a group of unknown perpetrators who starts smashing them.

6.title: Hoog Verraad: Part 1
6.plot: A dead night watchman is found at the bottom of an office building. The team quickly comes to the conclusion that it was not suicide. The man was strangled and was dead before he fell down. The investigation discovered that the night watchman was a secret on the track. Did someone to keep it quiet?

7.title: Hoog Verraad: Part 2
7.plot: A secret society deals with issues that can not bear the daylight. The detectives hunts a gone video sequences that can be proved. It is a quest that not only perilous risks entails, but also confidence in the police team severely to the test.

8.title: Lokaas
8.plot: Two young women who seem quite similar, are briefly disappeared one after another after they visited the same café. The investigation takes into account that the perpetrator strikes a third time. It is therefore decided to put out bait. One of the team members looks very similar to the two missing women.

9.title: Moed der Wanhoop
9.plot: A juvenile court is confronted by an armed boy standing on his doorstep. The boy claims that he and his girlfriend are allowed to keep their baby with them. The judge manages to keep him out the door, but then the boy goes on a desperate act with fatal consequences. The investigation team begins a race against the clock.

10.title: Solo
10.plot: All alarm bells go off when there is out of the barn of a farm hundreds of pounds of stolen fertilizer. The stuff is to manufacture heavy explosive material. The team must do everything to discover in time who stole the fertilizer and intends to carry out an attack .

1.title: Noodlot
1.plot: The owner of a neighborhood grocery store opens fire on two boys who raided his shop. One of the perpetrators dies during the shooting. The investigation team will start a search for the boy managed to escape and try to figure out where the weapons come from which the robbers have used. Fenna hears bad news in the hospital.

2.title: Ongewis
2.plot: During a liquidation on the street a boy was killed. The investigation team is committed to finding the culprit. Bram goes because of his personal commitment too far and he brings not only himself but also his colleagues at great risk. The situation of Fenna est course Irish still very uncertain and the demand est she ever again be the old one.

3.title: Uit de droom
3.plot: If Fenna after a long period of rehabilitation goes back to work, she notes that there are some things changed. Evert is now undercover in Berlin. The operation that is approaching, with all the risks that entails. Meanwhile, Bram has to defend himself in court because he did not obey the rules.

4.title: Patstelling
4.plot: The investigation is commanded to find an Afghan girl to detect. She is beaten on the run, because they will be put out of the country, Evert and Fenna go on research and it shows a tricky business.

5.title: Prooi
5.plot: A copycat is to copy the process of gruesome murders, the investigation team opens the hunt for the serial killer. Liselotte show ten years ago to have investigated the case. The new culprit it also provided her?

6.title: Onder druk
6.plot: The clubhouse of a motorcycle gang must conclude that the mayor is fatal; their house is shot. The investigation has struggled to get a grip on the matter has to do with the daughter of the Mayor anything?

7.title: Duivels genoegen
7.plot: A priest specializing in exorcism murdered one night. It appears that the offender has provided to representatives of the Roman Catholic Church. Then they discover to their horror that they seem to take on the devil in person.

8.title: Begin van het einde
8.plot: When a group of Syrian refugees arrive in a sports hall to be collected temporarily there, there will be a violent confrontation with local residents. In addition to a refugee life. The death of a man puts a chain of events that has dangerous consequences for the team. It soon becomes apparent that they are no one can rely in this case.

9.title: Veilige haven
9.plot: The discovery of a kidnapping and the existence of a chip containing deadly info triggers unprecedented events leading to the top of the government. Nothing is what is seems in this episode and the team heads unknowingly to the abyss.

10.title: Blinde vlek
10.plot: When a kidnapping goes almost wrong, the team is caught between a political and criminal gang all the way up through international terrorism. This ends with a bang and treason, death and destruction enters the team members...
